# Vue Component Standards

## Template Structure
- Use `<template>` then `<script setup lang="ts">` order
- No `<style>` blocks — use Tailwind utility classes exclusively (exceptions: POS animation keyframes)
- Use semantic HTML elements where appropriate

## Script Setup
- Always use `<script setup lang="ts">`
- Import types with `import type { X } from "~/lib/types"`
- Use `definePageMeta({ middleware: "auth" })` on all authenticated pages
- Composables are auto-imported — no need to import `useAuth`, `useStore`, etc.
- Status badge colors: import from `~/lib/ui/statusColors` instead of duplicating maps

## Tailwind CSS — Art & Craft Theme (white-first)
- Design tokens in `frontend/app/assets/css/main.css` `@theme`
- Surfaces: `surface` (#f6f9fc), `paper` (#ffffff) — Soft Sky white-first palette
- Primary: soft sky blue (`primary-400` #6b9eb8), Accent: soft teal
- Craft cards: use `<UiCraftCard variant="tag|polaroid|stitched|kraft|canvas|ticket|label|paper">` or CSS classes `craft-card craft-card--{variant}`
- Variants:
  - **paper** — lined notebook paper
  - **tag** — price tag with hole
  - **polaroid** — photo frame (use on POS product tiles via `craft-tile-polaroid`)
  - **stitched** — dashed border with corner dots
  - **kraft** — light kraft paper texture
  - **canvas** — grid weave texture
  - **ticket** — perforated ticket notches
  - **label** — sticker with folded corner
- Component classes: `.card` (legacy paper), `.btn-primary`, `.btn-secondary`, `.input`, `.badge`, `.pill-active`, `.pill-inactive`
- Status badges: import from `~/lib/ui/statusColors`

## Modals
- Use `<Teleport to="body">` for modals
- Backdrop: `craft-modal-backdrop craft-modal-backdrop--center` (or `--top`)
- Panel: `craft-modal-panel craft-modal--{stitched|paper|tag|ticket|label|canvas}` or `<UiCraftModal>`
- Close on backdrop click: `@click.self="showModal = false"`

## Data Loading
- Fetch data in `onMounted()` hook
- Show loading spinner while fetching
- Handle empty states gracefully
